<h1 class="doc-page-title">Enterprise Reporting</h1>
<p class="doc-page-lead">Enterprise reporting provides portfolio-wide visibility of performance metrics, functional standards compliance, and strategic alignment across the DfE digital portfolio.</p>

<h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>

<p>Enterprise reporting in COMPASS enables central operations teams and leadership to monitor and report on portfolio-wide performance, compliance, and strategic alignment. This includes enterprise-level metrics, functional standards assessments, and strategic objective tracking.</p>

